article_title: Ready or not, Mammoths and FXFL are returning pro football to Omaha

og.description: FXFL Commissioner Brian Woods will be in Omaha this week as the first-year league officially takes off, and Wednesday night his eyes will mostly be on the temporary football field wedged into the TD Ameritrade Park stadium that’s built for baseball.
